=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Notification for New Unsynchronized Product in Printcart</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .content {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
            background-color: #2f79c9;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #4ca1e6;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .center-container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        img {
            width: 80%;
        }

        .instructions {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
<div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            Dear {{ $json.name }},<br>
            <div>
                <p class="intro">I hope this message finds you well.</p>
            </div>
            We noticed that you recently updated a new product but haven't configured the custom design zones yet. Our
            <strong>Side Templates</strong>
            feature allows you to define design zones on different sides of a product and reuse them across multiple
            products with the same printing options.</p>
            <div>
                <h2 class="title">Set Up Custom Product</h2>
        <h3 class="subtitle">How to Set Up Your Side Template:</h3>
        <ol class="instructions">
            <li>Name the template.</li>
            <li>Specify product size (width and height).</li>
            <li>Set design area size (width and height) and margins (top and left).</li>
            <li>Choose background (image, color, or transparent).</li>
            <li>Select design area shape (rectangle or circle/ellipse).</li>
            <li>Show cut lines and safe zones if needed.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="conclusion">Please log in to your Printcart Dashboard and set up your Side Template for your latest product to ensure consistency and save time on future updates.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center-container">

            <a href="https://dashboard.printcart.com/product/{{ $json.uuid}}" style="color: #fff" class="button">Go to
                Product Detail</a>
        </div><br>
    </div>
</body>

